import { Image, Text, View } from "react-native"
import tw from "twrnc"

export default () => {
    return( 
    <View style = {tw`flex h-full w-full`}>
        <View style = {tw`h-full w-1/2 flex flex-col`}>
            <Text style = {tw`text-center`}>
                WELCOME BACK
            </Text>
        </View>
        <View>
            <Image />        
        </View>
    </View>
)}
